# RECT Inequality operator

Implements the inequality operator (!=).

```csharp

```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| deviceInfo1 | Operand 1. |
| deviceInfo2 | Operand 2. |

## Return Value

Returns true if `deviceInfo1` is not equal to `deviceInfo2`; false otherwise.
